title: Tech baseball to complete road swing Tuesday at JMU - VT hokiesports.com
content: Tech baseball to complete road swing Tuesday at JMU  VT hokiesports.com
description: Completing its first road swing of the 2022 season, the Virginia Tech baseball team (10-4) will seek a return to winning form on Tuesday, March 15, when Tech pays in-state foe James Madison (8-8) a visit at Veterans Memorial Park in Harrisonburg.
